movie_night.title: Movie Night!
movie_night.description: Why go out? Enjoy the cinematic experience from the comfort of your own living room with these big-screen movies and your favorite actors!

289816.title: Ghost In The Shell
289816.description: See the groundbreaking original before the release of the live-action remake starring Scarlett Johansson! It is 2029 and a female cyborg hunts a hacker who robs humans of their memories.

300448.title: Death At A Funeral
300448.description: After the unexpected death of a British patriarch, the dead man’s secrets leave the rest of his family with comical complications.

306935.title: Lars and The Real Girl
306935.description: A delusional young man strikes up an unconventional relationship with a doll he finds on the Internet in this weird and warm comedy.

312179.title: Get Shorty
312179.description: A gangster goes to Hollywood to collect a debt and becomes a big-time producer when he realizes the movie business runs a lot like the mob.

312424.title: Ronin
312424.description: A team of international mercenaries and ex-special operatives is hired to track down and steal a mysterious briefcase in this action-thriller.

313931.title: Stir of Echoes
313931.description: After being hypnotized, Tom (Kevin Bacon) is haunted by terrifying visions that seem to be sending him a message from beyond.

316459.title: Cube
316459.description: Seven strangers find themselves imprisoned in a seemingly endless maze filled with deadly traps and must fight to escape,  despite the odds.

316461.title: Hard Candy
316461.description: A 14-year-old girl turns the tables on her would-be predator in this psychological thriller.

321856.title: The Blair Witch Project
321856.description: A trio of filmmakers trek to uncover an urban legend, becomes an excursion into heart-stopping terror, in the original "found footage" horror.

348932.title: Escape Plan
348932.description: An incarcerated structural engineer teams up with another inmate to break out of a top-secret, high-security prison in this non-stop action-thriller.

356528.title: Bowling for Columbine
356528.description: This documentary examines gun violence in the U.S. in relation to other countries, including the specific events that led to the Columbine massacre.

396732.title: Short Term 12
396732.description: Grace, a young supervisor at a foster care facility for at-risk teenagers, takes on the crises of two new residents while going through her own.

399691.title: Requiem for a Dream
399691.description: The lives of four people intertwine in this gut-wrenching, hypnotic tale of addiction and the devastation it has on their lives and those around them.

400849.title: Sunshine Cleaning
400849.description: A once-popular single mother-turned-maid gets a new lease on life when she gets into the lucrative world of crime scene cleanup with her sister’s help.

401466.title: Four Weddings and a Funeral
401466.description: An Englishman meets an American woman at a wedding, but his inability to express his feelings forestalls any chance at love, until they meet again...and again.

404623.title: Battle Royale
404623.description: A group of students from a Japanese high school are forced to compete in a battle, killing one another until only one is left standing.

405451.title: Rescue Dawn
405451.description: Based on the true story of a captured German-American fighter pilot in the Vietnam War who plans a daring escape after suffering abuse by his captors.

437414.title: Tucker & Dale vs. Evil
437414.description: A group of college kids mistake Tucker and Dale for killer hillbillies and, when one goes missing, the misconception grows—along with the body count.

438023.title: I Saw the Devil
438023.description: A gifted government agent embraces his role as a ruthless vigilante after a prolific and sadistic murderer goes after someone he loves.

438042.title: Goon
438042.description: A bouncer looking for purpose takes his fighting skills to the hockey rink where his epic brawls could make him a star—if he can learn how to skate.

441470.title: Super Size Me
441470.description: Documentarian Morgan Spurlock explores the consequences on his health of a one-month diet consisting solely of items from the McDonald's menu.

448257.title: Amores Perros
448257.description: A horrific car accident connects the lives of three strangers: a lovesick dog fighter, an injured supermodel and a hitman running from his past.

448663.title: Leaving Las Vegas
448663.description: Determined to end it all, a committed drinker picks Vegas as his last stop, but he finds comfort with a kind prostitute who needs help of her own.

451666.title: Iron Sky
451666.description: The Nazis set up a secret base on the dark side of the moon in 1945 where they hide out and plan to return to power in 2018.

453693.title: Four Lions
453693.description: Four idiotic terrorists push their fuzzy dreams of jihad to the breaking point, as their beliefs and methods clash, in this far-out British farce.

456876.title: Bad Lieutenant: Port of Call New Orleans
456876.description: In the wake of Hurricane Katrina, a detective investigates the murders of several Senegalese immigrants.

456923.title: The Iceman
456923.description: Based on a shocking true story, a family man goes to great lengths to keep his work as a ruthless hitman a secret from the people he loves.

462517.title: The Illusionist
462517.description: In 19th century Vienna, a magician uses his talents to win the love of a noble woman but makes an enemy of the Crown Prince, now his romantic rival.

466212.title: Submarine
466212.description: A teenage boy aims to fulfill two dreams: to lose his virginity by his 16th birthday and to extinguish the flame between his mom and her ex-lover.

467588.title: The Man From Earth
467588.description: When colleagues throw a farewell bash for a retiring professor, the scholar reveals that he's had a stranger and far, far longer past than they knew.

476644.title: The Boondock Saints
476644.description: Irish brothers try to clean up Boston’s underworld by knocking off gangsters and become local folk heroes, as an FBI agent traces their bloody trail.

478798.title: Hellraiser
478798.description: This cult classic tells the story of an unfaithful wife and her dead lover. The chilling nightmare introduces the iconic demon Pinhead.

479932.title: Paris, Je T’aime
479932.description: Go beyond the postcard of Paris in this anthology of 20 films exploring many aspects of life, love, romance, drama and people in the City of Lights.

480291.title: Triangle
480291.description: A woman's yacht trip turns to terror when she hits a storm in and her group is forced to board a seemingly deserted ocean liner to get to safety.

487757.title: Monster
487757.description: This true story of a woman with a tortured past traces her path from prostitution, to hopeful love, to vengeful murder, to becoming a serial killer.

505794.title: Train to Busan
505794.description: Relentless terror marks the fight for survival as a massive zombie outbreak in South Korea leaves survivors on an infected train from Seoul to Busan.

507469.title: August: Osage County
507469.description: A dysfunctional mother’s emotional wounds against her adult children come to light as her family arrives at her Oklahoma home after a relative dies.

507477.title: The Ghost Writer
507477.description: A writer agrees to author the memoirs of a former Prime Minister only to learn that he is a war criminal and that his first writer was found dead.

507626.title: Sing Street
507626.description: Set in 1980s Dublin, a teen outcast forms a band with some of his friends to escape his strained family life and impress the mysterious girl he likes.

512252.title: We Need to Talk About Kevin
512252.description: In this suspenseful and gripping psychological thriller, a mother contends for years with the increasing malevolence of her first-born child, Kevin.

517750.title: The Conjuring
517750.description: Terrifying true story of a family attacked by paranormal, hostile events in their home in 1971, a disturbance only two paranormal experts could fix.

520213.title: Train to Busan (Dubbed)
520213.description: A father and his estranged daughter are trapped on a speeding train full of fellow passengers when a zombie virus breaks out in South Korea.

523697.title: Only God Forgives
523697.description: A remorseful man with a shady past, who longs to escape his role in Bangkok's gritty criminal underbelly, gets sucked into a brutal cycle of revenge.

524652.title: Coherence
524652.description: When eight friends gather for a dinner party on the night of an astronomical event, a series of unusual circumstances tests their relationships.

525069.title: The Mountain II
525069.description: After training in a covert special operations squad, two unlikely best friends begin their first mission to rescue an ISIS-captured reporter in Iraq.

526368.title: The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo
526368.description: In this adaptation of Stieg Larsson's novel, hacker Lisbeth Salander teams up with a journalist to investigate a murder connected to a rich family.

539677.title: Lion
539677.description: A young man makes an emotional journey to reconnect with his birth family in India after being tragically separated from them years earlier.

543161.title: Apocalypto
543161.description: A Mayan warrior braves the treacherous jungle to fight off attacking members of an opposing tribe in order to save his family.

543896.title: Reign Over Me
543896.description: A man shattered by the loss of his family in the 9/11 attacks in New York City rekindles a life-changing relationship with his old college roommate.

543987.title: Parker
543987.description: Based on the Donald E. Westlake novels, a thief works by a code of integrity and makes it his mission to avenge all that cross him or work dirty.

545561.title: Orphan
545561.description: A couple mourning the loss of their unborn baby adopt a little girl, except her new mom suspects something is disturbingly wrong with the child.

552216.title: Get the Gringo
552216.description: When a career criminal is nabbed by Mexican authorities and placed in a tough prison, he must  learn to survive, with the help of a young boy.

557519.title: After Earth
557519.description: Following a crash landing on Earth, a young boy and his estranged father must make an arduous journey and survive the elements to signal for help.

568896.title: Seven
568896.description: The final case for a retiring detective and his rookie partner follows a serial killer using the Bible’s seven deadly sins to target his victims.

569769.title: Pandorum
569769.description: Panic and terror come fast as two astronauts wake up in an empty spacecraft with no memory of what happened - except that an evil entity is waiting.

571822.title: Ringu
571822.description: A determined aunt investigates how her niece died in such a sudden and unexplainable way. She uncovers a videotape with devastating consequences.

577525.title: Eden Lake
577525.description: A British couple takes a trip to a private and isolated lake quarry for a vacation, only to be targeted by a lurking mob of psychotic teenagers.

579275.title: Hunt for the Wilderpeople
579275.description: Comic dynamite about a rebellious city kid who takes off with his gruff foster uncle in the New Zealand bush just as a manhunt begins to catch them.

579647.title: Fahrenheit 9/11
579647.description: The definitive exposé revealing how and why the Bush Administration manufactured evidence to invade war in Iraq following the 2001 terrorist attacks.

580532.title: Lucky Number Slevin
580532.description: A mysterious man is roped into a dangerous feud between two rival crime kingpins, neither of whom can step foot outside for fear of assassination.

582027.title: Killing Them Softly
582027.description: When a duo of inept crooks are hired to rob a mob-run poker game and crush the local criminal economy, vengeance is sought via a reluctant hitman.

582081.title: Vicky Cristina Barcelona
582081.description: Two American women are taken in by the splendor of Spain, but not as much as they are drawn to a rugged painter and his sultry former lover.

585148.title: Mallrats
585148.description: Male best friends, dumped by their girlfriends, spend the day strategizing at a local mall, in this funny, crude, and screamingly offensive offering.

588499.title: I Saw the Devil (Dubbed)
588499.description: An elite federal agent becomes violently and darkly obsessed with a serial killer’s demise after the man murders his pregnant fiancée in cold blood.

589111.title: The Lost Boys
589111.description: Sleep all day. Party all night. Never grow old. Never die. When a woman and her sons move to a California town, they discover the fun of vampire life.

589292.title: The Mask
589292.description: Jim Carrey’s superstar role as a kind and meek bank teller who gets super powers from a Nordic mask and becomes a totally s-s-s-smokin’ hero!

590035.title: Trollhunter (Dubbed)
590035.description: Three student filmmakers learn of a man who slays trolls for the Norwegian government. They risk everything to understand more about this odd world.

593782.title: Deep Blue Sea
593782.description: A scientist using genetically altered shark tissue to regenerate human brains fights for her life when the huge sharks breach her deep-sea station.

594095.title: Horrible Bosses
594095.description: The comedy smash about three co-workers who decide, after a lot of liquor, to get rid of their awful bosses and only manage to make things way worse.

602253.title: Jupiter Ascending
602253.description: The visionaries of ‘The Matrix’ films return with the thrilling story of a genetically engineered tracker who informs a woman of her cosmic destiny.

602506.title: Slither
602506.description: When an alien organism attacks a small town, a devoted wife must accept that her husband has transformed from the man she married.

608219.title: Gone in 60 Seconds
608219.description: To save his kid brother’s life from the mob, legendary retired car thief Memphis Raines will have to steal 50 cars and he has just one night to do it.

610966.title: The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen
610966.description: A team of fantastical superheroes from literary tales are assembled by a notorious adventurer in order to save the planet from annihilation.

616097.title: La Dosis
616097.description: Marcos is an experienced nurse. He works in the night shift of a provincial private clinic. He is applied and professional but has a secret: in some extreme cases he applies euthanasia. Gabriel, a new nurse, shakes the sector: he is young, intelligent and beautiful. Seduces everyone. He soon deciphers Marcos' secret by progressively taking control of his life. Marcos retracts until he discovers that Gabriel also kills, but capriciously. That revelation will force him to confront Gabriel, Marcos knows that only by exposing his true identity will be able to stop him.

617476.title: The Guardian
617476.description: A jaded Coast Guard trainer butts heads with an arrogant young recruit, as the two prepare for deadly missions and daunting rescues.

618279.title: Ace Ventura: When Nature Calls
618279.description: Jim Carrey returns in this hilarious sequel as Ace Ventura, back from a spiritual quest and on the case to find a rare and sacred white African bat.

620886.title: The Road
620886.description: Following an apocalyptic event, a father and son travel through North America’s dangerous terrain in the hopes of reaching the ocean.

620914.title: Death Defying Acts
620914.description: Set in 1926 England, this is the story of Harry Houdini having a torrid affair with a psychic, who is secretly working on conning the magician.

621683.title: Ace Ventura: Pet Detective
621683.description: When the mascot for football’s Miami Dolphins is stolen, a wacky detective goes undercover, underwater, and in over his head, to get his man or beast.

624927.title: Night of the Living Dead (In Color)
624927.description: A group of strangers struggles to fend off an attack of bloodthirsty zombies while barricading themselves inside a rural Pennsylvania farmhouse.

629523.title: Kings
629523.description: Amidst the fiery chaos of the Rodney King riots, a foster mother of 12 desperate to keep her family safe seeks help from her eccentric neighbor.

631121.title: The Man Who Killed Don Quixote
631121.description: A world-weary executive meets a man who believes he truly is "Don Quixote," who invites him on an adventure that combines fantasy and reality.

637111.title: ATL
637111.description: Inside an Atlanta roller rink, four hip hop-loving teens face life-changing turning points as they prepare for what comes next after high school.

637552.title: Out of the Furnace
637552.description: When his ex-Marine little brother disappears after joining a notorious crime syndicate, a Rust Belt steel worker gets armed and goes after him.

637827.title: Don Jon
637827.description: A Jersey guy addicted to porn meets a charming and beautiful woman whom he hopes to pursue a real relationship with, but his habits get in the way.

639309.title: 99 Homes
639309.description: A newly laid-off construction worker and single dad is forced to take a job working for the real-estate broker who heartlessly evicted his family.

639313.title: The Infiltrator
639313.description: Based on a true story, a U.S. federal agent goes deep inside the inner workings of a notorious drug trafficking cartel in order to take it down.

639315.title: Knight of Cups
639315.description: A successful and self-indulgent Los Angeles screenwriter ambles through a world of wild parties and women in a quest to find love and himself.

640031.title: Blackfish
640031.description: Award-winning documentary about the ethics of taking killer whales captive, especially after a loving trainer’s public death in a Sea World enclosure.

642254.title: The Girl with All the Gifts
642254.description: In a bleak future, mankind has succumbed to a fungus that turns everyone into flesh-eating monsters, until an immune child is discovered.

642272.title: I'm Not There
642272.description: The multifaceted life of Bob Dylan is examined through several variations of his own personality and career, embodied by six different characters.

642290.title: Rob Zombie's Halloween
642290.description: This remake of the classic finds Michael Myers after he’s released from a 17-year stay at the mental institution, already on a new killing spree.

643412.title: Nosferatu
643412.description: Much to the chagrin of his new bride, a German real estate agent is sent to Transylvania to purchase a castle owned by a count with a shadowy secret.

647082.title: Doomsday
647082.description: Nearly 30 years after a deadly epidemic swept through Scotland, a commander and her crew search for an antidote when the virus emerges in London.

654055.title: The Jerk
654055.description: Steve Martin makes his film-starring debut in the wacky comedy hit The Jerk. From rags to riches... to rags, the laughter never stops!

655132.title: Phenomenon
655132.description: An ordinary man discovers he has been endowed with unusual powers of intelligence and perception.

657037.title: Land of the Lost
657037.description: Comedy genius Will Ferrell stars as a has-been scientist, who gets more than he bargained for, when his expedition takes a wrong turn into hilarity.

658066.title: Riding in Cars With Boys
658066.description: Set in 1965, a 15-year-old girl with dreams of becoming a writer gets pregnant and enters a failed marriage with the baby’s drug-addicted father.

658082.title: To Die For
658082.description: Suzanne is dead set on being a famous TV reporter. When her husband asks her to give up her dream, she plots against him with a love-struck teenager.

663440.title: Dead Man Down
663440.description: A hitman for a New York crime lord is seduced and blackmailed by a victim seeking retribution who leads him on a violent and cathartic revenge spree.

663814.title: The Sisters Brothers
663814.description: Brothers and assassins Eli and Charlie Sisters pursue a prospector across the American Northwest in this witty reimagining of the cinematic Western.

664742.title: Speed
664742.description: A city bus with a bomb aboard is set to explode if it falls under 50 mph. An L.A. officer must help one of the passengers steer the bus to safety.

665877.title: Season of the Witch
665877.description: Two 14th-century Crusaders are tasked with routing a suspected witch to a distant monastery to let monks determine if she caused the Black Plague.

666313.title: The General
666313.description: When his locomotive is seized by spies, a rejected engineer decides to prove his worth by single-handedly recapturing and returning the train.

670407.title: The Fifth Element
670407.description: Director Luc Besson's extravagantly-styled, outrageous sci-fi tale of good against evil set in an unbelievable twenty-third century world.

672282.title: Jumanji
672282.description: Two children find and play a magical board game, releasing a man who has been trapped in it for decades and a host of wild and exotic creatures.

672284.title: Pixels
672284.description: An unlikely group of former '80s video game champions step up to save the world from an alien invasion in this visually spectacular action-adventure.

676660.title: The Babadook
676660.description: A mother struggles to protect her son from an evil supernatural entity that has escaped the pages of a children's book and is lurking in their home.

676665.title: The Death of Stalin
676665.description: Follows the wild scramble for power inside the Council of Ministers upon the sudden illness and death of Soviet dictator Joseph Stalin in 1953.

676695.title: Terminal
676695.description: A mystery inside a train terminal ensnares a dying teacher, two assassins on a mission, an enigmatic janitor and a waitress leading a double life.

676725.title: Boyhood
676725.description: Richard Linklater's acclaimed hit, filmed over twelve years with the same cast, is a groundbreaking celebration of life, growing up, and parenting.

676860.title: Bone Tomahawk
676860.description: When a group of individuals kidnaps settlers from a small town, an unlikely team of gunslingers, led by Sheriff Hunt, sets out to bring them home.

678881.title: Paul Blart: Mall Cop
678881.description: When a shopping mall is taken over by a gang of organized crooks, it's up to a mild-mannered security guard to save the day.

680230.title: Cassandra's Dream
680230.description: Two financially strapped brothers face a moral dilemma when their rich uncle offers to pay them to "eliminate" a business associate.

680568.title: Super
680568.description: A super-entertaining action fantasy about a down-on-his-luck fry cook who becomes a homegrown masked avenger and puts an end to crimes.

680736.title: Journey to the Center of the Earth
680736.description: An Icelandic expedition goes horribly wrong for a scientist and crew trapped in a cave and plunged into unimagined worlds against an erupting volcano.

680865.title: Unforgiven
680865.description: After more than a decade living in peace a former gunslinger, lured by a huge bounty, regresses into the cold-blooded killer he once was.

682190.title: Hesher
682190.description: After losing his mom in a car crash and drifting further from his forlorn dad, 10-year-old T.J meets Hesher, who makes his life even more chaotic.

682615.title: The Bourne Ultimatum
682615.description: Jason Bourne flees a new generation of skilled CIA operatives in a non-stop race around the globe while seeking the truth behind his mysterious past.

682626.title: Get Him to the Greek
682626.description: Aspiring music exec Aaron Green has just 72 hours to deliver rock legend Aldous Snow to LA, navigating a minefield of mayhem to get there.

682628.title: The Bourne Legacy
682628.description: Agent Aaron Cross uses his genetically enhanced skills to evade the CIA after Jason Bourne's actions lead to the termination of his black ops program.

685920.title: Brawl in Cell Block 99
685920.description: After he's fired from his mechanic gig, a hot-tempered ex-boxer enters the drug-running game which lands him in the battleground of a brutal prison.

688268.title: The Book of Eli
688268.description: Driven by commitment and guided by a belief in something greater than himself, a warrior not by choice but necessity, does what he must to survive.

694227.title: The Rundown
694227.description: A wild action-adventure about a bounty hunter named Beck, who's searching for a rebellious mobster's son and a priceless treasure in the Amazon.

694396.title: It
694396.description: In the town of Derry, Maine, seven young kids band together to stop a new killing cycle of an ancient, shape-shifting predator they can only call It.

696806.title: A Walk to Remember
696806.description: North Carolina teens Landon Carter and Jamie Sullivan are thrown together after one gets into trouble and is sentenced to community service.

698965.title: The Jackal
698965.description: An engaging suspense thriller about a ruthless assassin hired to eliminate a powerful, high-ranking official in the U.S. government.

698980.title: Dead Silence
698980.description: After the murder of his wife, a man returns to his hometown and uncovers the terrifying legend of Mary Shaw, a cursed ventriloquist from the 40s.

701396.title: Lamborghini: The Man Behind the Legend
701396.description: This thrilling, high-speed biopic reveals Ferruccio Lamborghini’s dream of making the world’s fastest car—and beating rival Enzo Ferrari to it.

705944.title: Babylon A.D.
705944.description: A ruthless mercenary is hired to smuggle a woman from the post-apocalyptic confines of Eastern Europe to the glittering megalopolis of New York City.

711013.title: Mid90s
711013.description: A 13-year-old spends his summer navigating a troubled home life and skating with a crew of new friends.

712894.title: The Help
712894.description: In 1960s Mississippi, a Southern girl turns her small town on its ear when she interviews African-American maids who have worked for white families.

720844.title: Dead Poets Society
720844.description: John Keating, a charismatic English professor, uses poetry to breathe new life into his students at a strict, all-boys prep school.

723810.title: Cell 211
723810.description: When a rookie prison guard is trapped in a cell during a violent riot, he must convince the prisoners he is one of them or face certain death.

723828.title: The Best Offer
723828.description: An eccentric and lonely art auctioneer becomes obsessed with a reclusive heiress he can’t see and who’s hired him to value her family’s collection.

724340.title: The Autopsy of Jane Doe
724340.description: Coroners are mystified by an unidentified corpse until a series of terrifying events makes it clear that cadaver Jane Doe is not actually dead.

724345.title: Identity Thief
724345.description: A hilarious blockbuster hit about an accounts representative who has one week to clear his name after a con artist steals his identity.

724349.title: The Scorpion King
724349.description: The spectacular Mummy series explodes into a new realm of non-stop action following the epic story of the most feared warrior of the ancient world.

724377.title: Downfall
724377.description: Traudl Junge, the final secretary for Adolf Hitler, tells of the Nazi dictator's final days in his Berlin bunker at the end of World War II.

724420.title: The Way Back
724420.description: A band of convicts stages an escape from a World War II Siberian gulag and embarks on a 4,000-mile journey on foot across five countries to freedom.

724713.title: Blue Is the Warmest Color
724713.description: A young French student finds love and affection for the first time with a lover when she begins a passionate relationship with a free-spirited woman.

724777.title: Frances Ha
724777.description: A late-20s New York woman dreams of being a dancer but is only an apprentice for a dance company. As she reaches adulthood, she finds herself.

100000001.title: Kubo and the Two Strings
100000001.description: After accidentally summoning an evil spirit, Kubo must recover his fallen samurai father’s mystical weaponry and discover his own magical powers.

100000089.title: Enter the Void
100000089.description: An American drug dealer living in Tokyo takes a psychedelic, acid trip-like journey into the afterlife when he’s killed in a deal gone bad.

100000170.title: Maze Runner: The Death Cure
100000170.description: In this epic conclusion, Thomas leads the Gladers on their final mission to break into the legendary Last City—the deadliest maze of all.

100000218.title: The Secret in Their Eyes
100000218.description: A recently retired criminal court investigator writes a novel based on a twenty-five-year-old unresolved rape and murder case, which still haunts him.

100000270.title: Official Secrets
100000270.description: Featuring a world-class ensemble cast, this gripping true-life thriller follows a spy gone rogue, who risks everything to stop an unjust war.

100000440.title: Gremlins 2: The New Batch
100000440.description: The gremlins are back and they’ve taken up residence in a Manhattan skyscraper. When the rules are broken, the Big Apple will never be the same.

100000720.title: I Now Pronounce You Chuck & Larry
100000720.description: In order to receive domestic partner benefits, two straight Brooklyn firefighters are forced to improvise as love-struck newlyweds.

100000724.title: Bruce Almighty
100000724.description: An encounter with God leaves a frustrated, wannabe news anchor for a Buffalo TV network with divine power and a life-altering challenge.

100000844.title: Exam
100000844.description: When eight candidates enter a windowless room to compete for a job at a mysterious and powerful company, the stakes soon become life or death.

100000850.title: Booksmart
100000850.description: About to graduate, two best friends try to cram four years of fun into one night after spending their high school years entirely focused on studying.

100000935.title: Paul
100000935.description: During a road trip to visit famous UFO sites, two sci-fi geeks encounter a wisecracking alien named Paul who is on the run from federal agents.

100000941.title: Mary and Max
100000941.description: Mary and Max are two misfits who become long-distance pen pals in this touching animated film about unlikely friendship and overcoming loneliness.

100001407.title: Flipped
100001407.description: “Somewhere between confusion and absolute terror,” 8th grader Bryce Loski begins to fall hard for the pesky girl who’s pined for him since age seven.

100001413.title: Matchstick Men
100001413.description: The streetwise teen daughter he never knew existed suddenly turns a neurotic con artist’s two-man team in small-time crime into a family business.

100001495.title: Eight Below
100001495.description: Stranded in Antarctica due to an unforgiving winter storm, a team of sled dogs must survive together until their determined trainer can rescue them.

100001593.title: Shaft
100001593.description: After his friend’s untimely death, cyber security expert John Shaft Jr. teams up with his estranged father to search the city’s criminal underbelly.

100001594.title: Rampage
100001594.description: When a group of animals becomes vicious after a genetic experiment goes awry, a primatologist must find an antidote to avert a global catastrophe.

100001596.title: Mortal Kombat
100001596.description: An MMA fighter with a mysterious dragon birthmark learns that he’s been chosen to fight for Earthrealm in the final battle against the evil Outworld.

100001597.title: It: Chapter Two
